Ubwina Nama Na Menshi (Bemba)
Akantu kalikele.  Abantu balikele nga fino ifyo twaikala.

Ubwina nama, bwalilongene.  Amenshi yalipwile.  Ilyo ubwina nama bwaikele, bwatile, “bane apo twalongana, uwingebusha amenshi mu bucinga ninani?”  Iyoo, pangeni seko.

Bwalipangile seko ubwina nama, Insofu, ba Cisongo, shonse inama apo shapela.  Elyo baebele ukutila, “bane uwala tampilapo ulwimbo ninani?  Uwakuti ebushe ubucinga amenshi?”

“Iyoo niba Nsofu.”

Ba Nsofu bapalama.  Elyo babula no lwimbo:

We bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
we bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
ba Nsofu mukulu, bawisha ingoshi,
bwina nama,
cimpindu bwina nama,
pindulukaee bwina nama.

Awe nakalya amenshi yemoneka.

Ati, “beteni ba Nsefu bese.”  Ba Nsefu bapalama.

We bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
we bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
ba Nsefu mukulu, bawisha ingoshi,
bwina nama,
cimpindu bwina nama,
pindulukaee bwina nama. 

Nakalya, tayewile. 

Ba bula ba Mbo-o iseni, baimba ngefi fine.  Ba Fulwe bakoti, “Mukwai nebo kuti naimba.”

Abati, “webo ico cimo ca ipipa niwebo wingeusha amenshi?” Kanshi bulenifye Imfubu iyapa mumana eingebusha. Awe babula naba Mfubu, baisa ikala.  “Aleni ba Mfubu ulwimbo!”

We bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
we bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
ba Mfubu mukulu, bawisha ingoshi,
bwina nama,
cimpindu bwina nama,
pindulukaee bwina nama.

Nakalya yemoneka.

“Alaa, tukocita shani?  Aleni ba Kalulu ni mwe mwacenjela.”  Ba Kalulu baisa, baikala.

We bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
we bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
ba Kalulu mukulu, bawisha ingoshi,
bwina nama,
cimpindu bwina nama,
pindulukaee bwina nama. 

Nakalya. 

Awe Fulwe na kambi waisa, “Mwe baice, lekeni mwafwilisheko!” Abati, “iyoo mwebo, lekeni Fulwe ngale eukoleta amenshi.”  Abati, “ngata wa bikemofye amenshi umu, walamona ifyo tule kucita.”  Awe Fulwe wakalafuka, wakwisa kwikala na pakati.

We bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
we bucinga bwa imbileko abange,
bwina nama,
ba Fulwe mukulu, bawisha ingoshi,
bwina nama,
cimpindu bwina nama,
pindulukaee bwina nama  

Awe na menshi mu bucingafye uunhu, yaisula. 

Kanshi Fulwe eo bapitile no kutwala ku mfumu, ba mulepwilako neca buta. 

Epo na komfwilile mukwaiUbwina Nama Na Menshi (Bemba)
